                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/7210</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consul
                            <persName type="to">Edwards</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>
                        </placeName>, <lb/>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-01-14T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 14, 1916, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Urgent. Department learns serious situation prevailing at Madera. Urgently
                    request adequate force be sent to that place for protection of foreigners
                    against bandits.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
